# ESP-IDF (examples/webH264's [env:webH264]) build/dependency artifacts.
# sdkconfig.defaults is the checked-in seed config; sdkconfig.<env> is generated
# from it plus ESP-IDF's own defaults on every build. dependencies.lock (IDF
# Component Manager) is intentionally kept for reproducible esp_h264 resolution.
sdkconfig.*
